725175f-a.title: Queens: 29th Street - 40th Avenue
725175f-a.text:
29th Street, east side, between 40th Avenue and 40th Road,
showing the First Reformod Church of Long Island City. It is an
old frame structuro with a newly-added brick front. The parsonage
appears in view 2.
P. L. Sporr  View 1: March 23, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS  View 2s Septomber 5, 1940

725176f-a.title: Queens: 29th Street - 40th Avenue
725176f-a.text:
29th Street, at the N.W. corner of 40th Avenue, showing
the south wall and rear of St. Patricks Roman Catholic Church.
The view is east on 40th Avenue toward 29th Street.
P. L. Sperr  March 23, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725322f-a.title: Queens: 40th Avenue - 29th Street
725322f-a.text:
40th Avenue, east from 29th Street to 3lst Street
(where the ''El' is seen) and Northern Boulevard.
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS  March 23, 1932
